## Attribution

This project was created specifically for Australian home networks and includes
optimizations for Australian internet infrastructure. The configuration
templates and documentation reflect Australian privacy laws, network topology,
and cultural considerations.

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and home use purposes. Users are
responsible for ensuring compliance with local laws and regulations regarding
DNS filtering, privacy, and network security in their jurisdiction.

For Australian users, please ensure compliance with:
- Privacy Act 1988
- Telecommunications Consumer Protections Code
- Australian Privacy Principles
- Any applicable state and territory legislation

The maintainers of this project are not responsible for any legal implications
of using this software. Users should consult with legal professionals if
uncertain about compliance requirements.

